{
  "stem": "9601.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The Russian soldier kept, you know, sort of let them only graze a certain amount.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we used to sit at the back, you know, to watch that they didn't go to the fields.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But we always sat on the hill of the forest to have command of the village.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "To see if any-- if they're gonna kill the Jew, if they're going to come after you, maybe you can have spot them before they get there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So we used to sit on the hill, you know, to-- to look out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Then-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] then 1 September of '42, we were notified by the mayor that they're gonna come and liquidate us.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So we came home that day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We came-- this all on-- on the QT.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "How we found out, or what how it went, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "What-- you know, what-- But I do know we came home, we had dinner.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Whatever we had-- something to eat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "My father, my mother told me, you take with you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Get dressed.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Put on all the clothes you can put on yourself.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Don't carry a bundle, because a bundle is a deterrent.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But I had a little bundle, you know, clothes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I must have put on five or six shirts, you know, underpants, thermal underwear I had, couple other slacks, and a jacket-- you know, a warm jacket-- and a hat, and no gloves.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And something in the-- a couple shirts in the back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they told me-- now, this is already '42, I'm almost full 12 years old.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they said, you know, you go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You can go to this man, to Baranchuk and [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Timosh ?] and the Baranchuk the other one, and-- and another person's name I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And looking back now, these were all intellectuals.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
